{
  "stem": "19550.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was pretty well run down long before that, along about October or so of 1944, in other words, about eight, nine months into the camp period.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so weakened, as many others were before me and after me, that I had begun to give up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is, in fact, as the result of that, that I got to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sent to Dachau what they called in Germany a [INAUDIBLE] for recovery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not many people would have, in their right mind, undertaken to volunteer to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had reached the point, not physically, but emotionally and mentally, where I was at the verge of giving up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was, it was a very critical moment for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have described that in detail at, in the [INAUDIBLE] taping, I discovered one day when we were at, most unusually, at relative leisure in a camp, and I said to myself suddenly, you bastard.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Today you didn't think of your mother and sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that to me spelled the end of my humanity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I began to give up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Fortunately enough, apparently I still had enough mental reserves that with just a little bit of time in Dachau where I didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even though that maybe the food rations were smaller, at least I didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so maybe more of the calories stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I began to recover.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I was sent to [INAUDIBLE] got into the kitchen, which enabled me to have a little more food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And which enabled me also to bring some food out for others, including, most particularly, for our [INAUDIBLE] rabbi who insisted on remaining kosher.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so I recovered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I'm alive and only because of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
